text: Amna Fayyaz (born 2 August 2002) is a Pakistani professional squash player. As of May 2019, she was ranked number 110 in the world. She won the 2019 Pakistan Squash Circuit I professional tournament.http://thesquashsite.com/pakistan- circuit-1 ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani female squash players Category:Racket sportspeople from Rawalpindi Category:South Asian Games silver medalists for Pakistan Category:South Asian Games medalists in squash
